        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "> Could you please elaborate on how the `rev=nil` situation occurred?\r\n> \r\n> This should not happen, as lockfile is repaired on restart. So if this happens, it is the result of manual edit, which is prohibited. The relevant information about this problem and how to solve it would appear in `:checkhealth vim.pack`.\r\n\r\nThis happened when I was trying to port my existing `vim.pack` setup to a new machine. Admittedly I did have some errors in my configuration, but I definitely did not make any manual modifications.",
